<title>WAMARKET.RESTO</title>
<style>
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:'Segoe UI',Tahoma,sans-serif; }
:root {
    --vert: #1B8E3A; --vert-fonce: #0F5F24; --vert-clair: #4CAF50;
    --bleu: #1976D2; --bleu-fonce: #0D47A1;
